text: Kurchenko () is a rural locality (a selo) and the administrative center of Kurchensky Selsoviet, Narimanovsky District, Astrakhan Oblast, Russia. The population was 423 as of 2010. There are 4 streets. == Geography == It is located 49 km from Astrakhan, 81 km from Narimanov. == References == Category:Rural localities in Narimanovsky District
title: Kurchenko, Astrakhan Oblast
